	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Re: Tool that breaks up bitmap, removes duplicate tiles, etc</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><a href="http://pyxeledit.com/" class="postlink">Pyxel Edit</a><br />It can do everything in your list. (though the way it saves an array to a file may not be best for you. But whatever)<br />Import an image with 8x8 tile size. It will check for duplicates, even transformations. (Sadly you can't choose which transformations. For instance, You want it to check for X and Y flipped tiles but not rotations.)<br /><br />It's a pretty self explanatory program.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


